{
  "stem": "2718.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- we had a roof over our head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had nothing else but the roof over our head.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and the floor, the concrete floor, was-- was straw in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was-- that was everybody's bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the-- the sanitary was-- that is-- that is what I think were the first degradation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's when we really know what-- what degradation meant, because the-- the-- the sanitary arrangements were latrines.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were dug into the-- into the-- into the earth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was just one latrine for women and one latrine for men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was, I think, other people has lost-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] dignity-- has-- have lost their dignity and felt that we are not exactly being treated as VIPs.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people begin-- had begun to understand that we were in serious trouble.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they-- the treatment what we received there, the way the food was received there-- there was nobody had any food there anymore for-- left what they took-- what they had before.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because whatever there was, a little was consumed in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when you have one suitcase to carry, I don't think that many people would just think of carrying food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The others carried their own little belongings what they-- what they have to be able to change clothes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were also warned where when we left the ghetto that we'll be walking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We knew where Budakalasz was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So no, everybody knew that nobody could carry a huge, big suitcase for 10 kilometers or more.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So really, we went-- we-- we traveled light.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The authority, I think, the-- the police and-- and the Hungarian authorities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that actually was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the-- the speech you were given.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
